@startuml
title Legacy Material2 stdlib aliases
!include <material2.1.19/common>
!include <material2.1.19/folder_move>
!include <material2/folder>
MA_FOLDER_MOVE(#1565c0, 1, archive, rectangle, "Archive Folder")
MA_FOLDER(home, "Home Folder")
archive -> home : restore <$ma_folder_move{scale=2,color=#1565c0}> old include path
note over archive, home
